The first time I saw him, someone else was fighting and losing.  I ran to go lend a hand, but got in too late to save the lad.  Well, I finished of the mad erudite, and got the +% vs fire earring.  Someone going on a Nagy raid wanted fire saveing jewelry, and bought it for 40pp.  Now that I want one though, I can't seem to find this Erudite.<BR>
<BR>
Ok, just checking the original submission:  Do you really just kill alot of regular old Island Madmen to get him to spawn?  How many is alot?  what is the time frame you need to kill them in?  Island madmen are spawned by which again: spiders or snakes?<BR>
