	<tr>
		
			<td colspan="2" bgcolor="#DEDACB" background="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/tb_beige.gif">
		
				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				I have had no problem soloing the Island Madman since level 13.<BR>
I am now a 17 Mage and I have killed the Madman at least 6 times.<BR>
I have not died once.<BR>
At level 13 I used my water pet and a summoned snake fang for the pet.<BR>
I cast a fire shield on the pet and my self.<BR>
A few shock of blades spells, and he was toast.<BR>
<BR>
Mages level 14 or higher, should not fear this Mad Man, you should be able to take him solo.<BR>
Just watch out for the Cats.<BR>
<BR>
But why waste your mana and time with the Mad Man.<BR>
Kill the willows, the Gr's are worth at least 7-9 plat.<BR>
And you get double exp.<BR>
Exp for the kill, and exp for turning in the Gr's to the gypsies in N.Karana.<BR>
You will level a lot quicker and earn more cash,if you concentrate on the willows.<BR>
The Mad Man is a waste of time.<BR>
If you are bored with the Willows, fight the Zombie sailors.<BR>
At least you will get good exp, and a bronze weapon every once in awhile.<BR>
<BR>
That's my 2cp<BR>
Revolt. (Dragons Fellowship of the Lore)<BR>
17 Level Mage<BR>
The Rathe server
				</font>
			</td>

