			<td colspan="2" bgcolor="#DEDACB" background="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/tb_beige.gif">
		
				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				I had just leveled to 20, and felt the need to stop in Erud's crossing to make a few quick platinum by gathering greater lightstones.  All was well until to my utter amazement, an erudite madman began nuking me from afar.  I'd been to the isle many times in the past, and had never actually seen an erudite madman.  He already had me down to half hp before I could even find the slimey scum.  When I managed to near him, he started punching me for 36 points of damage at an alarmingly rapid pace.  I lost my level due to this psycho, even if he did con risky blue...I'm not sure if he's aggro like this to all races and classes, but he sure hates my Barbarian warrior.  Anyone know if this is faction related?  No one else seems to be assaulted without provoking the fight first.  If anyone knows, please don't hesitate to post.  I'd kind of like having to not watch my bum so closely.  Heh.  Be well.
				</font>
			</td>

	</tr>
	
